  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Phase II trial to determine the efficacy of Dose Adjusted-EPOCH-Rituximab regimen in children
      and adolescent with primary mediastinal large B cell lymphoma in terms of event free
      survival.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
